uliraellarai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lirael Larai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/28/02 10:18:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Agility</span><hr size=1> Igonre it, agility is 100% useless. As long as you are above 75 there is no real benefits to be gained from having it at all. <p>Lirael L'arai<BR>Crusader of Prexus<BR>Vazaelle<BR>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=88551</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usenchy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Senchy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 331<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/29/02 4:42:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Agility</span><hr size=1> Agreed, get agility at or over 75 and you are set.<br><br>More important is really trying to get sta at/over 100 so you don't suffer from fatique effects when swinging heavy weapons. <p>Senchy Solariatus60 Crusader of Rodcet Nife55 Chanter of Rodcet Nife (Tymbor)Dol Amroth<BR><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=79641>My Profile</a><BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubeldukil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Beldukil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 3722<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/29/02 6:24:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=334.topic&index=3